  "rationale": "Single sanctioned hero bookend reusing the seeded hero-display-over-staggered-media pattern verbatim (stack archetype, inverse surface, centered didone display title with the sole gold accent, measured copy bound verbatim, asset:null measured photography). The ONE varied axis is media max-width: the centered hero-media widens to a 9-column span (colStart 3, colSpan 9) versus the original ~6-col reading, while the original lower-edge media-over-media crossing is preserved by declaring overlap-media colSpan 4 with registration to hero-media's bottom edge at depthBaselines 10, z front. Palette, type tiers, spacing steps, and the overlap+stagger treatments are otherwise identical to the seed; novelty is adapt with seededFrom the project hero pattern."
